ji\" /></blockquote><br />\n竟然？師兄考過？<br />\n有咩推介</blockquote><br />\n<br />\ndick<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\ndicky<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"989c0def9851350dc733de0012108c2b39dceaaf","tid":471044,"uid":124173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T02:33:09.000Z","msg":"我覺得YY個mock好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無其他中文mock可以考慮"},{"pid":"77aae5849066c5dd23beb39ee70422dc96dfeba5","tid":471044,"uid":137912,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T02:37:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得YY個mock好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無其他中文mock可以考慮</blockquote><br />\n巴定絲?<br />\n如果係絲嘅話小妹可以資助你"},{"pid":"58824fe67fbf04f8eb5de0b0fb92636c5fb6c0cb","tid":471044,"uid":21503,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T02:42:04.000Z","msg":"math dick<br />\n份卷係比dse 難少少<br />\n但係真係學到野<br />\nmock 考到lv 5<br />\n結果dse 出黎係5**<br />\ndick哥考完仲有一份mock卷拎返去做<br />\n同埋有解卷班<br />\n遵理啲mock 改得hea到，仲要改唔晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果有補開dick哥真係會feel 到佢好有心教，even我補開video班，都有個好好既助教係到比人問野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2bcec9433d1be07f6b0d1be49e38f49ed8a3ed7","tid":471044,"uid":124173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T02:42:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我覺得YY個mock好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無其他中文mock可以考慮</blockquote><br />\n巴定絲?<br />\n如果係絲嘅話小妹可以資助你</blockquote><br />\n巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  屎忽岩唔岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"574d33849065a7ff9ce628f7f55964ededcf886b","tid":471044,"uid":137912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T02:57:55.000Z","msg":"<blo